title: ‘Atlanta’ Episode 14 and ‘Beverly Hills’ Episode 15
description:
Rachel begins this week’s 'Morally Corrupt' with a recap of Season 14 Episode 14 of ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta’, courtesy of Chelsea Stark-Jones (1:10). Rachel is then joined by Jodi Walker, who breaks down Season 12 Episode 15 of ‘The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills’ (25:29).
Host: Rachel Lindsay
Guests: Chelsea Stark-Jones and Jodi Walker
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
Theme Song: Devon Renaldo
